OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTV's Julie Goodyear slowly 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffading away, says husband  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The husband of Coronation Street       
OL,6, actress Julie Goodyear has said she is 
OL,7, "slowly fading away" following her     
OL,8, dementia diagnosis.                    
OL,10,FScott Brand told The Mirror newspaper  
OL,11,Fthat he missed his "fun-loving wife",  
OL,12,Fand said it was "extremely painful" to 
OL,13,Fwatch her deterioration.               
OL,15,FGoodyear, 81, played the               
OL,16,Fleopard-skin-loving barmaid Bet Lynch  
OL,17,Fin the soap.                           
OL,19,FBrand was speaking up in conjunction   
OL,20,Fwith a new Alzheimer's Society         
OL,21,Fcampaign, which the couple are backing.
